name: A Game Of Life
tagline: A Game Of Life implementation developed using HTML5 Canvas, FabricJS & Typescript
body: This is a Game Of Life implementation (devised by the british mathematician John Horton Conway in 1970) developed using HTML5 Canvas, FabricJS & Typescript. You can download it as an archive from here or browse the source in [Github](https://github.com/harindaka/GameOfLife). A powerpoint presentation on the same is also included.
